.SH NAME
grafana\-util\-access\-service\-account \- List, create, export, import, diff, or delete Grafana service accounts, and manage their tokens.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B grafana-util access service-account [\fIOPTIONS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
List, create, export, import, diff, or delete Grafana service accounts, and manage their tokens.
.IP \(bu 2
Inspect service\-account inventory.
.IP \(bu 2
Create or update service\-account bundles.
.IP \(bu 2
Generate or delete service\-account tokens.
